lobber any meaningful existing name with\nclientId. Preserve the existing persisted name on update when the caller\ndoesn't send one, falling back to clientId only if even the existing\nrecord has no name.\n\nAlso allow client_credentials in the grant-type allowlist. The DCR\nsystem registrar client is created with CLIENT_CREDENTIALS by\nOAuth2DcrService.init(); the UI showed no way to keep this valid on\nedit, so every PUT to that client returned 409. client_credentials is\na legitimate Spring Authorization Server grant type, adding it unblocks\nthe edit path.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"bc7949a771ea7702d94e29fb549085b5a2ac7cab","tree_id":"e024f7e0320502711802dfd2d59e0a5e3324ec3e","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:11:57Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://ap